<title>USA: Dendrite approves share purchase program.</title>
<headline>Dendrite approves share purchase program.</headline>
<dateline>MORRISTOWN, New Jersey 1997-02-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Dendrite International Inc said late Monday that its board had approved a share purchase program that may include open market purchases of up to $10 million based on market conditions.</p>
<p>The company said an initial $3 million in share purchases would begin after February 10.</p>
<p>Also on Monday the company reported a fourth quarter net loss of $3.3 million, or $0.29 per share, including non-recurring items, compared to a profit of $2 million, or $0.19 per share, in the year-ago quarter.</p>
<p>Dendrite closed down 1/4 on Monday at 8-7/8.</p>
<p>-- New York newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
